      <front>
         <div type="tipografia" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
            <p rend="writing-mode(horizontal-lr) text-orientation(sideways)" part="N">
               <s> Cromoscultura A.Traldi - Milano </s>
               <s>  N.01311 Languido abbandono L'abandoun </s>
               <s> PRODUZIONE ITALIANA </s>
            </p>
         </div>
      </front>
      <body>
         <div type="fronte" part="N" org="uniform" sample="complete">
            <figure>
               <head>Languido abbandono</head>
               <figDesc>In primo piano una coppia di innamorati appoggiati al tronco di un albero, 
                        sullo sfondo un gruppo di pecore. 
                  </figDesc>
            </figure>
         </div>
         <div type="retro">
            <div type="message">
               <opener>
                  <dateline>
                     <lb/>
                     <s>            Milano li 4/3-1917</s>
                  </dateline>
               </opener>
               <div type="postcard-body">
                  <p>
                     <lb/>            Mia buona Oliva<lb/>            Il tedio mi asfale qui a <lb/>            Milano dove si suol veni-<lb/>            re per obliare le disillusio-<lb/>            ni e le amarezze della vita.<lb/>            È il tuo pensiero costante, af-<lb/>            fettuoso che mi infonde <lb/>            la nostalgia della tua <lb/>            lontananza.<lb/>            Oliva, Oliva è l'amor tuo<lb/>            che mi oscura tutte le gioie <lb/>            della vita.... t'amo tanto <lb/>            tanto e mi strugge il desiderio <lb/>            d'esferti vicino.</p>
                  <p type="fronte"/>
               </div>
               <closer>
                  <s>
                     <lb/>Un bacio ardentisfimo <lb/>
                     <signed>
                        <persName>
                           <forename ref="Giovannino">Giovannino</forename>
                        </persName>
                     </signed>
                  </s>
               </closer>
            </div>
            <div type="postmark-postage">
               <ab/>
            </div>
            <div type="secondamano">
               <ab type="paratext" part="N">
                  <add>
                     <num type="cardinal"> 21 </num>
                  </add>
               </ab>
            </div>
         </div>
      </body>
